@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_wynkci(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (0.34 / v2)
    v2 = (0.77 * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.94) / tmp))
    v1 = (v0 + (v1 + (tmp + 0.71 + v1 + 0.99)))
    v1 = wp.cos(tmp)
    tmp = 0.56
    v0 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.71 + v2 + 0.62)) - (wp.sin(tmp + 0.56) * v0))
    data[tid] = v0
